description: Economic observability — pack vs tier consumption, model economics, developer value

panels.description: Daily Pollen consumption: Pack (green) vs Tier (orange). Tier % (red) = tier share of total. Excludes Dec 30–Jan 8 bug window. Affected by: $timeRange.

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  toStartOfInterval(start_time, INTERVAL 1 DAY) as time,
  sumIf(total_price, selected_meter_slug IN ('v1:meter:pack', 'local:pack')) as paid_cost,
  sumIf(total_price, selected_meter_slug IN ('v1:meter:tier', 'local:tier')) as free_cost,
  paid_cost + free_cost as classified_cost,
  if(classified_cost > 0, free_cost / classified_cost, 0) as subsidy_pct
FROM generation_event
WHERE $__timeFilter(start_time)
  AND environment = 'production'
  AND response_status >= 200 AND response_status < 300
  AND total_price > 0
  AND user_github_id != '241978997'
  AND (start_time < toDateTime('2025-12-30 16:59:45') OR start_time > toDateTime('2026-01-08 18:19:58'))
GROUP BY time
ORDER BY time

panels.title: Pack vs Tier Consumption Over Time

panels.description: Developer (secret/publishable) vs End-user (temporary) key usage. Early signal — only ~3 weeks of data. Affected by: $timeRange.

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  toStartOfInterval(start_time, INTERVAL 1 DAY) as time,
  sumIf(total_price, api_key_type IN ('secret', 'publishable') AND selected_meter_slug IN ('v1:meter:pack', 'local:pack')) as developer_paid,
  sumIf(total_price, api_key_type IN ('secret', 'publishable') AND selected_meter_slug IN ('v1:meter:tier', 'local:tier')) as developer_free,
  sumIf(total_price, api_key_type = 'temporary' AND selected_meter_slug IN ('v1:meter:pack', 'local:pack')) as enduser_paid,
  sumIf(total_price, api_key_type = 'temporary' AND selected_meter_slug IN ('v1:meter:tier', 'local:tier')) as enduser_free,
  developer_paid + developer_free as developer_total,
  enduser_paid + enduser_free as enduser_total,
  if(developer_total + enduser_total > 0, enduser_total / (developer_total + enduser_total), 0) as enduser_share_pct
FROM generation_event
WHERE $__timeFilter(start_time)
  AND environment = 'production'
  AND response_status >= 200 AND response_status < 300
  AND total_price > 0
  AND user_github_id != '241978997'
  AND (start_time < toDateTime('2025-12-30 16:59:45') OR start_time > toDateTime('2026-01-08 18:19:58'))
GROUP BY time
ORDER BY time

panels.title: BYOP Split: End-user vs Developer ⚠️

panels.description: Total users with any consumption (first use = signup proxy).

targets.rawSql: SELECT countDistinct(user_github_id) as active_users FROM generation_event WHERE environment = 'production' AND response_status >= 200 AND response_status < 300 AND total_price > 0 AND user_github_id != '' AND user_github_id != '241978997' AND (start_time < toDateTime('2025-12-30 16:59:45') OR start_time > toDateTime('2026-01-08 18:19:58'))

panels.title: Active Users (All Time)

panels.description: Users who used packs within 7 days of their first tier usage.

targets.rawSql: SELECT countIf(first_pack IS NOT NULL AND first_pack >= first_tier AND dateDiff('day', first_tier, first_pack) <= 7) as converted_7d FROM (SELECT user_github_id, minIf(start_time, selected_meter_slug IN ('v1:meter:tier', 'local:tier')) as first_tier, minIf(start_time, selected_meter_slug IN ('v1:meter:pack', 'local:pack')) as first_pack FROM generation_event WHERE environment = 'production' AND response_status >= 200 AND response_status < 300 AND total_price > 0 AND user_github_id != '' AND user_github_id != '241978997' AND (start_time < toDateTime('2025-12-30 16:59:45') OR start_time > toDateTime('2026-01-08 18:19:58')) GROUP BY user_github_id HAVING first_tier IS NOT NULL)

panels.title: Converted (≤7D)

panels.description: Users who used packs within 30 days of their first tier usage.

targets.rawSql: SELECT countIf(first_pack IS NOT NULL AND first_pack >= first_tier AND dateDiff('day', first_tier, first_pack) <= 30) as converted_30d FROM (SELECT user_github_id, minIf(start_time, selected_meter_slug IN ('v1:meter:tier', 'local:tier')) as first_tier, minIf(start_time, selected_meter_slug IN ('v1:meter:pack', 'local:pack')) as first_pack FROM generation_event WHERE environment = 'production' AND response_status >= 200 AND response_status < 300 AND total_price > 0 AND user_github_id != '' AND user_github_id != '241978997' AND (start_time < toDateTime('2025-12-30 16:59:45') OR start_time > toDateTime('2026-01-08 18:19:58')) GROUP BY user_github_id HAVING first_tier IS NOT NULL)

panels.title: Converted (≤30D)

panels.description: Conversion rate: users who converted within 7 days / all active users with tier usage.

targets.rawSql: SELECT if(total_users > 0, converted_7d / total_users, 0) as conversion_rate_7d FROM (SELECT count() as total_users, countIf(first_pack IS NOT NULL AND first_pack >= first_tier AND dateDiff('day', first_tier, first_pack) <= 7) as converted_7d FROM (SELECT user_github_id, minIf(start_time, selected_meter_slug IN ('v1:meter:tier', 'local:tier')) as first_tier, minIf(start_time, selected_meter_slug IN ('v1:meter:pack', 'local:pack')) as first_pack FROM generation_event WHERE environment = 'production' AND response_status >= 200 AND response_status < 300 AND total_price > 0 AND user_github_id != '' AND user_github_id != '241978997' AND (start_time < toDateTime('2025-12-30 16:59:45') OR start_time > toDateTime('2026-01-08 18:19:58')) GROUP BY user_github_id HAVING first_tier IS NOT NULL))

panels.title: Conversion Rate (7D)

panels.description: Per-model economics: total cost, pack/tier split, pack share %, and avg cost per request. Sorted by pack_share descending (most economically healthy first).

targets.rawSql: SELECT resolved_model_requested as model, sum(total_price) as total_cost, sumIf(total_price, selected_meter_slug IN ('v1:meter:pack', 'local:pack')) as paid_cost, sumIf(total_price, selected_meter_slug IN ('v1:meter:tier', 'local:tier')) as free_cost, if(total_cost > 0, paid_cost / total_cost, 0) as paid_share, if(count() > 0, total_cost / count(), 0) as avg_cost, count() as requests FROM generation_event WHERE $__timeFilter(start_time) AND environment = 'production' AND response_status >= 200 AND response_status < 300 AND total_price > 0 AND resolved_model_requested != '' AND user_github_id != '241978997' AND (start_time < toDateTime('2025-12-30 16:59:45') OR start_time > toDateTime('2026-01-08 18:19:58')) GROUP BY resolved_model_requested HAVING requests >= 1000 ORDER BY paid_share DESC LIMIT 50

panels.title: Model Economics Leaderboard

panels.description: Where does pack consumption come from? Ranked by absolute pack Pollen, not percentage.

targets.rawSql: WITH total_paid AS (SELECT sum(total_price) as total FROM generation_event WHERE $__timeFilter(start_time) AND environment = 'production' AND response_status >= 200 AND response_status < 300 AND total_price > 0 AND selected_meter_slug IN ('v1:meter:pack', 'local:pack') AND user_github_id != '241978997' AND (start_time < toDateTime('2025-12-30 16:59:45') OR start_time > toDateTime('2026-01-08 18:19:58'))) SELECT resolved_model_requested as model, sumIf(total_price, selected_meter_slug IN ('v1:meter:pack', 'local:pack')) as paid_cost, paid_cost / (SELECT total FROM total_paid) as pct_of_total_paid, countIf(selected_meter_slug IN ('v1:meter:pack', 'local:pack')) as paid_requests, if(paid_requests > 0, paid_cost / paid_requests, 0) as avg_paid_cost FROM generation_event WHERE $__timeFilter(start_time) AND environment = 'production' AND response_status >= 200 AND response_status < 300 AND total_price > 0 AND resolved_model_requested != '' AND user_github_id != '241978997' AND (start_time < toDateTime('2025-12-30 16:59:45') OR start_time > toDateTime('2026-01-08 18:19:58')) GROUP BY resolved_model_requested HAVING paid_cost > 0 ORDER BY paid_cost DESC LIMIT 20

panels.title: Top Models by Pack Usage

panels.description: Where does tier allocation go? Models consuming the most tier Pollen.

targets.rawSql: WITH total_free AS (SELECT sum(total_price) as total FROM generation_event WHERE $__timeFilter(start_time) AND environment = 'production' AND response_status >= 200 AND response_status < 300 AND total_price > 0 AND selected_meter_slug IN ('v1:meter:tier', 'local:tier') AND user_github_id != '241978997' AND (start_time < toDateTime('2025-12-30 16:59:45') OR start_time > toDateTime('2026-01-08 18:19:58'))) SELECT resolved_model_requested as model, sumIf(total_price, selected_meter_slug IN ('v1:meter:tier', 'local:tier')) as free_cost, free_cost / (SELECT total FROM total_free) as pct_of_total_free, countIf(selected_meter_slug IN ('v1:meter:tier', 'local:tier')) as free_requests, if(free_requests > 0, free_cost / free_requests, 0) as avg_free_cost FROM generation_event WHERE $__timeFilter(start_time) AND environment = 'production' AND response_status >= 200 AND response_status < 300 AND total_price > 0 AND resolved_model_requested != '' AND user_github_id != '241978997' AND (start_time < toDateTime('2025-12-30 16:59:45') OR start_time > toDateTime('2026-01-08 18:19:58')) GROUP BY resolved_model_requested HAVING free_cost > 0 ORDER BY free_cost DESC LIMIT 20

panels.title: Top Models by Tier Usage

panels.description: Developer economics scatter: X=tier consumption, Y=pack consumption. Top-right=high volume, bottom-right=tier-heavy, top-left=pack-efficient.

targets.rawSql: SELECT user_github_username as developer, sumIf(total_price, selected_meter_slug IN ('v1:meter:tier', 'local:tier')) as free_cost, sumIf(total_price, selected_meter_slug IN ('v1:meter:pack', 'local:pack')) as paid_cost FROM generation_event WHERE $__timeFilter(start_time) AND environment = 'production' AND response_status >= 200 AND response_status < 300 AND total_price > 0 AND user_github_username != '' AND user_github_id != '241978997' AND (start_time < toDateTime('2025-12-30 16:59:45') OR start_time > toDateTime('2026-01-08 18:19:58')) GROUP BY user_github_username HAVING (free_cost + paid_cost) >= 10 ORDER BY (free_cost + paid_cost) DESC LIMIT 100

panels.title: Developer Economics Scatter

panels.description: Apps ranked by economic health (pack share). Which apps drive pack usage vs consume tier?

targets.rawSql: SELECT api_key_name as app, sum(total_price) as total_cost, sumIf(total_price, selected_meter_slug IN ('v1:meter:pack', 'local:pack')) as paid_cost, sumIf(total_price, selected_meter_slug IN ('v1:meter:tier', 'local:tier')) as free_cost, if(total_cost > 0, paid_cost / total_cost, 0) as paid_share, count() as requests FROM generation_event WHERE $__timeFilter(start_time) AND environment = 'production' AND response_status >= 200 AND response_status < 300 AND total_price > 0 AND api_key_name != '' AND api_key_name != 'undefined' AND user_github_id != '241978997' AND (start_time < toDateTime('2025-12-30 16:59:45') OR start_time > toDateTime('2026-01-08 18:19:58')) GROUP BY api_key_name HAVING total_cost >= 100 ORDER BY paid_share DESC LIMIT 30

panels.title: App Economy Leaderboard

panels.description: ROUTER (pollen-router) internal service account usage. Left axis: Pollen amounts. Right axis: ROUTER % of total. Should trend DOWN as external usage grows.

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  toStartOfInterval(start_time, INTERVAL 1 DAY) as time,
  sum(total_price) as total_pollen,
  sumIf(total_price, user_github_id = '241978997') as router_pollen,
  if(total_pollen > 0, router_pollen / total_pollen, 0) as router_pct
FROM generation_event
WHERE $__timeFilter(start_time)
  AND environment = 'production'
  AND response_status >= 200 AND response_status < 300
  AND total_price > 0
  AND (start_time < toDateTime('2025-12-30 16:59:45') OR start_time > toDateTime('2026-01-08 18:19:58'))
GROUP BY time
ORDER BY time
